ram is essential for every designer, and with its wide spread of options and applications, this guide would quickly help beginners to learn how to use the basics of Photoshop CS5. Since there\'s already a number of guides, what makes our guide better than others? Our research showed us, that many of the existing guides are either too voluminous, use very bad examples, or didn\'t cover topics like illustrations and graphics. Our job was to filter important topics to receive a light handbook and practise every tutorial using good photography and artworks.</p><p>In addition to the book, we created an online platform for students, where they could upload their works, give feeback and their own tutorials.</p><p>Content of our thesis:</p><p>- Research<br>- Conception<br>- Logo Design<br>- Guide Design &amp; Tutorials<br>- Webdesign<br>- Production</p><p>&nbsp;</p>\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:9:\"full_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";s:1121:\"<p>For our final thesis my friend and colleague Justyna Matuszewska and I made this <em>Photoshop CS5 Guide for students</em>.</p>\n<p>The idea was to create an assistance for design students, who haven\'t worked with Photoshop before. The program is essential for every designer, and with its wide spread of options and applications, this guide would quickly help beginners to learn how to use the basics of Photoshop CS5. Since there\'s already a number of guides, what makes our guide better than others? Our research showed us, that many of the existing guides are either too voluminous, use very bad examples, or didn\'t cover topics like illustrations and graphics. Our job was to filter important topics to receive a light handbook and practise every tutorial using good photography and artworks.</p>\n<p>In addition to the book, we created an online platform for students, where they could upload their works, give feeback and their own tutorials.</p>\n<p>Content of our thesis:</p>\n<p>- Research<br />- Conception<br />- Logo Design<br />- Guide Design &amp; Tutorials<br />- Webdesign<br />- Production</p>\n<p> </p>\n\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:20:\"field_project_images\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:10:{i:0;a:15:{s:3:\"fid\";s:3:\"221\";s:3:\"uid\";s:1:\"4\";s:8:\"filename\";s:12:\"thesis01.jpg\";s:3:\"uri\";s:30:\"public://projects/thesis01.jpg\";s:8:\"filemime\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";s:6:\"524897\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"timestamp\";s:10:\"1357921100\";s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";s:11:\"rdf_mapping\";a:0:{}s:16:\"image_dimensions\";a:2:{s:5:\"width\";s:4:\"1000\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"784\";}s:3:\"alt\";N;s:5:\"title\";N;s:5:\"width\";s:4:\"1000\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"784\";}i:1;a:15:{s:3:\"fid\";s:3:\"228\";s:3:\"uid\";s:1:\"4\";s:8:\"filename\";s:12:\"thesis02.jpg\";s:3:\"uri\";s:30:\"public://projects/thesis02.jpg\";s:8:\"filemime\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";s:6:\"384895\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"timestamp\";s:10:\"1358108325\";s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";s:11:\"rdf_mapping\";a:0:{}s:16:\"image_dimensions\";a:2:{s:5:\"width\";s:4:\"1000\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"784\";}s:3:\"alt\";N;s:5:\"title\";N;s:5:\"width\";s:4:\"1000\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"784\";}i:2;a:15:{s:3:\"fid\";s:3:\"229\";s:3:\"uid\";s:1:\"4\";s:8:\"filename\";s:12:\"thesis03.jpg\";s:3:\"uri\";s:30:\"public://projects/thesis03.jpg\";s:8:\"filemime\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";s:6:\"433824\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"timestamp\";s:10:\"1358108340\";s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";s:11:\"rdf_mapping\";a:0:{}s:16:\"image_dimensions\";a:2:{s:5:\"width\";s:4:\"1000\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"784\";}s:3:\"alt\";N;s:5:\"title\";N;s:5:\"width\";s:4:\"1000\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"784\";}i:3;a:15:{s:3:\"fid\";s:3:\"230\";s:3:\"uid\";s:1:\"4\";s:8:\"filename\";s:12:\"thesis04.jpg\";s:3:\"uri\";s:30:\"public://projects/thesis04.jpg\";s:8:\"filemime\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";s:6:\"666729\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"timestamp\";s:10:\"1358108353\";s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";s:1